  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Urinary retention is a common complication of epidural analgesia. Auriculotherapy could
      prevent this complication. This study will be performed among men receiving thoracic epidural
      analgesia after thoracic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
